---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Eklavya Tuition Classes" description="Learn about Eklavya Tuition Classes — our mission, vision, and story since 2009.">
  <div class="space-y-16">

    <section>
      <h1 class="font-serif font-normal leading-[var(--leading-display)] tracking-[var(--tracking-display)] mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-signifier); font-size: var(--text-display); color: var(--color-ink);">
        About Us
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-body-lg)] text-[var(--color-ash)] max-w-3xl leading-[var(--leading-body-lg)]" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body-lg);">
        Established in 2009, Eklavya Tuition Classes has been a trusted name in academic coaching for over a decade. Located in the heart of Sita Rama bazaar, we provide focused, high-quality education for students from Class 1 to Class 10.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="bg-[var(--surface-fog)] rounded-3xl p-10">
        <h2 class="text-[var(--text-heading-sm)] font-serif font-medium mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-signifier); font-size: var(--text-heading-sm); color: var(--color-ink);">
          Our Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-body)] text-[var(--color-graphite)] leading-[var(--leading-body)]" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body);">
          To provide every student with a strong academic foundation through personalized coaching, fostering both intellectual growth and character development.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[var(--surface-fog)] rounded-3xl p-10">
        <h2 class="text-[var(--text-heading-sm)] font-serif font-medium mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-signifier); font-size: var(--text-heading-sm); color: var(--color-ink);">
          Our Vision
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-body)] text-[var(--color-graphite)] leading-[var(--leading-body)]" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body);">
          To be the most trusted tuition center in the region — known for academic excellence, dedicated faculty, and nurturing an environment where every child thrives.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-[var(--text-heading)] font-serif font-normal leading-[var(--leading-heading)] tracking-[var(--tracking-heading)] mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-signifier); font-size: var(--text-heading); color: var(--color-ink);">
        Our Story
      </h2>
      <div class="bg-[var(--surface-warm-tint)] rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--text-body)] text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body);">
          What began as a small initiative to help a handful of students has grown into a thriving learning community. Over the past 15 years, Eklavya has helped hundreds of students build confidence, improve their grades, and excel in their academic journeys.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-body)] text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body);">
          Our approach is simple: understand each child's unique learning style, provide patient guidance, and create a supportive environment where questions are encouraged and curiosity is celebrated.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-body)] text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-relaxed" style="font-family: var(--font-sohne); font-size: var(--text-body);">
          With a team of 4 dedicated faculty members, we offer coaching in all major subjects across both Telugu and English mediums — ensuring that every child receives the attention and instruction they deserve.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
